(134, '39516', 'tt0382721', 'The Fallen', ' Drama War', 'Northern Italy, Autumn 1944, the last days of World War II. Germans and Italians try to defend the Gothic Line and fight the partisans who support the inexorable advance of the US Army.', '/lrTFGBECgZ77JeG8VXomBy4U0jD.jpg', '2004', 106, '4.80', 6, ''),
