(219, '57800', 'tt1667889', 'Ice Age: Continental Drift', ' Animation Comedy Adventure Family', 'Manny, Diego, and Sid embark upon another adventure after their continent is set adrift. Using an iceberg as a ship, they encounter sea creatures and battle pirates as they explore a new world.', '/6NSFKyOz7ppsd0KY6g4HInIZ53P.jpg', '2012', 88, '6.30', 5989, ''),
