(221, '8355', 'tt1080016', 'Ice Age: Dawn of the Dinosaurs', ' Animation Comedy Family Adventure', 'Times are changing for Manny the moody mammoth, Sid the motor mouthed sloth and Diego the crafty saber-toothed tiger. Life heats up for our heroes when they meet some new and none-too-friendly neighbors – the mighty dinosaurs.', '/cXOLaxcNjNAYmEx1trZxOTKhK3Q.jpg', '2009', 94, '6.70', 6378, ''),
(222, '15035', 'tt0085542', 'Fire and Ice', ' Animation Fantasy Science Fiction', 'In this animated tale, a tiny village is destroyed by a surging glacier, which serves as the deadly domain for the evil Ice Lord, Nekron. The only survivor is a young warrior, Larn, who vows to avenge this act of destruction. The evil continues, however, as Nekron\'s palace of ice heads straight towa', '/iu3JlLPOk5RUXVJpifkxv9739oo.jpg', '1983', 81, '6.30', 122, ''),
